        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span class="mo">/</span>
       </div>
       <span class="mi">ω</span>
       <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
      </div>
     </div> at three exemplary 
     <span class="italic">ϕ</span>. (
     <span class="italic">b</span>) Surrogate oscillator model (
     <a ref-type="disp-formula" rid="RSOS172078M3x7" href="#RSOS172078M3x7">3.7</a>) that mimics the subcritical Hopf bifurcation when the parameter 
     <span class="italic">ν</span> is increased. In the three-dimensional plot, 
     <div class="inline-formula">
      <div id="IM7" class="math">
       <div class="msub">
        <span class="mi">P</span>
        <span mathvariant="normal" class="mi">∞</span>
